567
00:24:00,299 --> 00:24:02,023
What do you need a boyfriend for?

568
00:24:02,106 --> 00:24:04,506
I mean, if you get a boyfriend,
and he bullies you,

569
00:24:04,672 --> 00:24:06,593
I will still have to teach him a lesson.

570
00:24:11,586 --> 00:24:13,544
The key now is

571
00:24:13,627 --> 00:24:16,383
Meng Meng needs to

572
00:24:16,466 --> 00:24:18,743
break free from the circle she has drawn

573
00:24:18,826 --> 00:24:19,826
around herself.

574
00:24:20,520 --> 00:24:23,560
She needs to regain
confidence and dignity.

575
00:24:23,732 --> 00:24:25,023
Dad, Mum,

576
00:24:25,106 --> 00:24:27,237
let her come to our medical centre.
I'll help you.

577
00:24:27,586 --> 00:24:29,957
If she can't go to school now,
let her join the apprentice class.

578
00:24:30,040 --> 00:24:31,277
I will guide her in her study.

579
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:33,383
If her parents are busy,
she can stay at our place.

580
00:24:33,466 --> 00:24:34,510
I will take care of her.

581
00:24:36,106 --> 00:24:37,586
If we do that,

582
00:24:38,106 --> 00:24:39,623
do you know how great the risks are?

583
00:24:39,706 --> 00:24:40,706
Yes.

584
00:24:41,106 --> 00:24:42,715
She is my patient in the first place.

585
00:24:43,066 --> 00:24:45,675
Last time, it was because of my mistake
that she almost died.

586
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:47,934
This time, I must take
full responsibility for her.

587
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:51,600
No.

588
00:24:52,106 --> 00:24:53,106
Your dad is right.

589
00:24:53,547 --> 00:24:54,852
This is a huge responsibility.

590
00:24:55,706 --> 00:24:57,623
None of us

591
00:24:57,706 --> 00:24:59,272
can keep an eye on her every second.

592
00:24:59,466 --> 00:25:01,336
What if something unexpected
happens to her?

593
00:25:03,466 --> 00:25:04,343
How are we going
to answer to her parents?

594
00:25:04,426 --> 00:25:06,466
Mum, King of Medicine,
Sun Si Miao, once said

595
00:25:06,706 --> 00:25:08,223
that when someone seeks help
for their illness or adversity,

596
00:25:08,306 --> 00:25:09,983
we must not inquire about
their social status or wealth.

597
00:25:10,066 --> 00:25:11,466
All beings are equal.

598
00:25:11,586 --> 00:25:12,904
Our knowledge and action
must be the same.

599
00:25:12,987 --> 00:25:14,507
These are different matters.

600
00:25:16,706 --> 00:25:17,743
How does this girl

601
00:25:17,826 --> 00:25:18,826
look like?

602
00:25:19,547 --> 00:25:20,547
Dad...

603
00:25:22,826 --> 00:25:24,346
From what you've just said,

604
00:25:24,706 --> 00:25:28,023
