is both wealthy and beautiful.

605
00:25:28,106 --> 00:25:29,226
Your intentions

606
00:25:29,586 --> 00:25:31,223
are good,

607
00:25:31,306 --> 00:25:33,586
but people may misunderstand that

608
00:25:33,987 --> 00:25:35,147
you have ulterior motives.

609
00:25:36,186 --> 00:25:37,186
Grandpa.

610
00:25:39,513 --> 00:25:40,672
Now he's mad at me.

611
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:49,560
Hello?

612
