Who?

616
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:17,960
No, I mean,

617
00:26:18,872 --> 00:26:20,472
I acted bravely

618
00:26:20,747 --> 00:26:21,867
and did a righteous deed

619
00:26:22,186 --> 00:26:23,466
today.

620
00:26:24,186 --> 00:26:25,946
It's a matter of honour for me.

621
00:26:26,466 --> 00:26:29,547
I'm bringing you along
to share in this glory, you know?

622
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:30,895
Go home and pack your stuff.

623
00:26:30,978 --> 00:26:32,022
You are staying with us.

624
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:33,120
Staying with...

