628
00:26:41,946 --> 00:26:42,863
They...

629
00:26:42,946 --> 00:26:44,106
They, they, they.

630
00:26:44,426 --> 00:26:45,707
They are they, you are you.

631
00:26:47,372 --> 00:26:48,372
Let me tell you,

632
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,503
