649
00:27:19,586 --> 00:27:20,586
Master!

650
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:25,200
Don't you know how many rooms we have?

651
00:27:28,886 --> 00:27:29,967
Other people

652
00:27:30,466 --> 00:27:32,507
