653
00:27:32,706 --> 00:27:34,066
while you and your son

654
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:38,479
bring home people.

655
00:27:39,878 --> 00:27:42,400
With two more people living here,
I have to do more chores.

656
00:27:43,867 --> 00:27:45,027
Both of you

657
00:27:45,346 --> 00:27:47,651
