leaving all the jobs for me.

658
00:27:47,946 --> 00:27:49,343
They are big girls.

659
00:27:49,426 --> 00:27:50,687
You don't need to serve them.

660
00:27:51,226 --> 00:27:52,725
They can take care of themselves.

661
00:27:53,627 --> 00:27:54,627
Both of

662
00:27:54,747 --> 00:27:55,747
these girls

663
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,200
are worrisome.

664
00:27:57,946 --> 00:27:59,729
You said they can
take care of themselves.

665
00:28:00,106 --> 00:28:01,586
But I still have to

666
00:28:02,106 --> 00:28:03,103
worry about them.

667
00:28:03,186 --> 00:28:04,814
I have my reasons,

668
00:28:04,897 --> 00:28:06,417
asking Tou Tou to stay with us.

669
00:28:06,946 --> 00:28:08,023
Look at Meng Meng,

670
00:28:08,106 --> 00:28:10,367
