to keep an eye on her all the time.

671
00:28:10,826 --> 00:28:13,143
Who can keep an eye on her
when she sleeps at night?

672
00:28:13,226 --> 00:28:16,226
Who in our family
can accompany her all the time?

673
00:28:16,627 --> 00:28:17,667
With Tou Tou around,

674
00:28:18,466 --> 00:28:19,814
they can look after each other.

675
00:28:20,066 --> 00:28:21,066
Sun Tou Tou

676
