677
00:28:23,106 --> 00:28:24,367
And you want to count on her?

678
00:28:25,066 --> 00:28:27,306
I'm with Tou Tou this time.

679
00:28:28,226 --> 00:28:30,140
It's true that
she shouldn't have hit people,

680
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:32,520
but she was in the right.

681
00:28:36,987 --> 00:28:37,987
All right.

682
00:28:38,306 --> 00:28:39,654
