694
00:29:04,306 --> 00:29:05,939
What we pursue isn't just knowledge,

695
00:29:06,627 --> 00:29:08,383
but like-mindedness.

696
00:29:08,466 --> 00:29:09,946
Look, I even married you

697
00:29:11,080 --> 00:29:12,211
to be closer to my master.

698
00:29:13,203 --> 00:29:14,426
I ensured that

699
00:29:14,706 --> 00:29:16,343
I live under the same roof as my master.

700
00:29:16,426 --> 00:29:17,383
You see,

701
00:29:17,466 --> 00:29:18,464
if I'm teaching through words and deeds,

702
00:29:18,547 --> 00:29:20,466
I need a recipient for it, don't I?

703
00:29:21,946 --> 00:29:23,066
Ren Xin Zheng.

704
00:29:25,946 --> 00:29:27,251
You called me by my full name.

705
00:29:27,547 --> 00:29:28,946
I think you're mad for real now.

706
00:29:30,466 --> 00:29:31,466
I'm sorry.

707
00:29:32,226 --> 00:29:33,226
Sorry.

708
00:29:35,066 --> 00:29:36,466
Tell me what you did wrong.

709
00:29:38,346 --> 00:29:39,586
This is the fourth

710
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:42,360
major philosophical question in life.

711
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:03,296
(The young seedlings are just planted.)

712
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:07,160
(The crops are newly sown.)

713
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:10,927
(Spring rain is as precious as oil.)

714
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:18,133
(Grain Rain)

715
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:20,930
What are you doing here?

716
00:30:21,013 --> 00:30:22,863
Haven't you already worked
two night shifts in a row?

717
00:30:22,946 --> 00:30:24,863
The flu this time is too severe.

718
00:30:24,946 --> 00:30:26,143
Liu's child is also sick.

719
00:30:26,226 --> 00:30:28,143
There is really no one else
to take over the shift.

720
00:30:28,226 --> 00:30:29,103
As a single man,

721
00:30:29,186 --> 00:30:30,103
I have to go

722
00:30:30,186 --> 00:30:31,186
wherever I am needed.

723
00:30:31,426 --> 00:30:33,166
All right. Stay here
and keep watch then.

724
00:30:33,306 --> 00:30:35,480
I'm going to the ward.
It can't be left unattended.

725
00:30:36,066 --> 00:30:36,863
By the way,

726
00:30:36,946 --> 00:30:38,623
pay extra attention
to the child in bed 34

727
00:30:38,706 --> 00:30:39,907
who has pneumonia.

728
00:30:40,226 --> 00:30:41,464
He had a seizure last night.

729
00:30:41,547 --> 00:30:43,437
His mum almost had
a breakdown because of it.

730
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:44,520
