731
00:30:51,346 --> 00:30:53,129
Dr Peng, a child needs a lumbar puncture.

732
00:30:53,426 --> 00:30:54,623
Got it. I'll be right over.

733
00:30:54,706 --> 00:30:55,706
Okay.

734
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,000
Jason, right?

735
00:30:58,125 --> 00:30:59,125
I'm Dr Peng.

736
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:01,023
I will perform
a lumbar puncture on you later.

737
00:31:01,106 --> 00:31:03,889
We'll start by administering
anaesthesia, so it won't be painful.

738
00:31:04,066 --> 00:31:05,466
As a brave man,

739
00:31:05,627 --> 00:31:06,907
you will be brave, right?

740
00:31:07,346 --> 00:31:08,184
You won't cry, right?

741
00:31:08,267 --> 00:31:09,906
Come on, fist bump.

742
00:31:11,586 --> 00:31:13,503
-Step back!
-Mummy! Don't touch me!

743
00:31:13,586 --> 00:31:15,226
What are you doing to my child...

744
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:18,841
Mummy, I don't want to do this.

745
00:31:19,706 --> 00:31:21,863
Madam, maybe you should
talk to your son first

746
00:31:21,946 --> 00:31:23,251
before we perform the surgery.

747
00:31:24,627 --> 00:31:25,627
Sorry about this.

748
00:31:26,466 --> 00:31:29,226
Jason, you are a good boy, right?

749
00:31:29,946 --> 00:31:30,944
Want to go out and play?

750
00:31:31,027 --> 00:31:32,186
Thanks, Peng.

751
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:35,023
If it weren't for you, I would
have been beaten to death today.

752
00:31:35,106 --> 00:31:36,466
I learned this the hard way.

753
00:31:36,826 --> 00:31:37,826
You are an intern.

754
00:31:37,987 --> 00:31:39,306
You've got a lot to learn.

