766
00:32:05,826 --> 00:32:07,174
Would you like to come with us?

767
00:32:09,946 --> 00:32:11,706
You see, we are ready to depart now.

768
00:32:11,946 --> 00:32:12,946
Come with us.

769
00:32:15,466 --> 00:32:16,466
Come.

770
00:32:16,826 --> 00:32:17,826
Don't be afraid.

771
00:32:23,987 --> 00:32:24,987
Easy.

772
00:32:27,627 --> 00:32:29,410
You see, it's right there.
Let's go there.

773
00:32:35,066 --> 00:32:36,066
Mrs Xu,

774
00:32:36,226 --> 00:32:37,787
