783
00:32:56,426 --> 00:32:57,426
Dr Song,

784
00:32:58,066 --> 00:32:59,066
sorry about this,

785
00:32:59,426 --> 00:33:00,706
but I have to leave too.

786
00:33:01,106 --> 00:33:02,023
Here's the thing.

787
00:33:02,106 --> 00:33:03,626
We received a sudden notification

788
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:06,143
