both parents to be present?

793
00:33:14,027 --> 00:33:15,383
You see, Xu isn't here too.

794
00:33:15,466 --> 00:33:16,503
When he comes back,

795
00:33:16,586 --> 00:33:17,586
we will come together.

796
00:33:21,706 --> 00:33:23,106
Meng Meng is your child.

797
00:33:23,627 --> 00:33:25,064
If you prioritize all the things

798
00:33:25,147 --> 00:33:26,706
ahead of your child,

799
00:33:26,946 --> 00:33:28,381
then there is nothing I can't do.

800
00:33:29,186 --> 00:33:31,586
