00:34:08,107 --> 00:34:09,238
He's my friend. It's okay.

816
00:34:10,547 --> 00:34:11,383
Relax. It's fine.

817
00:34:11,466 --> 00:34:14,264
Meng Meng, you're finally here!

818
00:34:14,347 --> 00:34:15,744
Hold on, hold on, Tou Tou.

819
00:34:15,827 --> 00:34:17,623
-Don't you remember me, Meng Meng?
-Meng Meng, listen.

